Module scenebuilder.core
Package com.oracle.javafx.scenebuilder.core.editor.selection

Class Selection

java.lang.Object
com.oracle.javafx.scenebuilder.core.editor.selection.Selection
@Component
@Scope("document")
@Lazy
public class Selection
extends Object
Selection class represents the selected objects for an editor controller.

Selected objects are represented an instance of AbstractSelectionGroup.
